item.title: These 10 Photos Were Taken Moments After Assassinations. They're As Profound As They Are Eerie.
item.description: There are moments in history when it seemed like the world stopped. Like on Friday, November 22nd, a young President Kennedy was driving through Dealey Plaza in Dallas, TX.
